#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.nav.ul.li:355-13
#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.h3:633-5
msgid "Frequently Asked Questions"
msgstr "Dažnai užduodami klausimai"

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.p:360-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"productname\">{productname}</span> allows you to create and "
"edit office documents text documents, spreadsheets and presentations "
"directly in your browser, in a simple and straight-forward way. You can work "
"alone on a document, or collaboratively as part of a team."
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"productname\">{productname}</span> leidžia paprastai ir "
"aiškiai kurti ir redaguoti „Office“ dokumentus – tekstinius dokumentus, "
"skaičiuokles ir pristatymus – tiesiai naršyklėje. Galite dirbti su dokumentu "
"savarankiškai arba bendradarbiauti kaip komandos dalis."

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.ul.li:367-7
msgid ""
"Each user gets assigned a color. The cursor of each user will be shown in "
"the assigned color. Note: you will see your cursor as black, blinking "
"cursor, although others will see you with a different color."
msgstr ""
"Kiekvienam vartotojui priskiriama spalva. Kiekvieno vartotojo žymeklis bus "
"rodomas priskirta spalva. Pastaba: jūs matysite savo žymeklį kaip juodą, "
"mirksintį, nors kiti jus matys kitos spalvos."

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.ul.li:368-7
msgid ""
"You can jump to the cursor of a user by clicking on the name (or avatar) of "
"the user. It is possible to follow the editor."
msgstr ""
"Galite pereiti prie vartotojo žymeklio spustelėdami vartotojo vardą (arba "
"avatarą). Galima sekti redaktorių."

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.ul.li:369-7
msgid ""
"<span class=\"productname\">{productname}</span> notifies you with a small "
"notification in the footer when a new user enters or when a user leaves."
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"productname\">{productname}</span> praneša jums mažu pranešimu "
"poraštėje, apie naujo vartotojo prisijungimą arba vartotojo išėjimą."

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.p:375-30
msgid ""
"<span class=\"productname\">{productname}</span> uses modern browser "
"resources to adapt the user interface to the size of the viewing area, "
"including small screens found in mobile devices. The interface is composed "
"of:"
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"productname\">{productname}</span> naudoja modernių naršyklių "
"išteklius, kad pritaikytų vartotojo sąsają prie žiūrėjimo srities dydžio, "
"įskaitant mažus mobiliųjų įrenginių ekranus. Sąsają sudaro:"

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.p:377-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"def\">The document area:</span> The application area shows the "
"document contents, either spreadsheets, presentations or text documents."
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"def\">Dokumento sritis:</span> Programos srityje rodomas "
"dokumento turinys – skaičiuoklės, pristatymai arba tekstiniai dokumentai."

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.p:380-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"def\">The menu bar:</span> The main menu is at the top and "
"includes many options, such as commands for printing, editing, viewing, and "
"other advanced commands. You can hide the menu bar by clicking the hide icon "
"<span class=\"w2ui-icon fold icon-size\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"hide menu "
"bar\" title=\"Hide menu bar\"></span> on the far right. To show it again, "
"click the show icon <span class=\"w2ui-icon unfold icon-size\" role=\"img\" "
"aria-label=\"show menu bar\" title=\"Show menu bar\"></span>."
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"def\">Meniu juosta:</span> Pagrindinis meniu yra viršuje ir "
"jame yra daug parinkčių, pvz., spausdinimo, redagavimo, peržiūros ir kitos "
"išplėstinės komandos. Meniu juostą galite paslėpti spustelėdami slėpimo "
"piktogramą <span class=\"w2ui-icon fold icon-size\" role=\"img\" aria-"
"label=\"hide menu bar\" title=\"Hide menu bar\"></span>, esančią tolimajame "
"dešiniajame kampe. Norėdami ją vėl rodyti, spustelėkite rodymo piktogramą "
"<span class=\"w2ui-icon unfold icon-size\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"show "
"menu bar\" title=\"Show menu bar\"></span>."

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.p:383-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"def\">Context menus:</span> On clicking with the right mouse "
"button, a menu appears with commands associated with the underlying object."
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"def\">Kontekstiniai meniu:</span> Spustelėjus dešinįjį pelės "
"mygtuką, atidaromas komandų meniu, susietas su esamu objektu."

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.p:386-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"def\">The toolbar:</span> The toolbar contains the most used "
"options for daily editing. Toolbar buttons are dynamic, meaning that their "
"state (on or off) depends on different factors."
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"def\">Įrankių juosta:</span> Įrankių juostoje yra dažniausiai "
"naudojamos kasdienio redagavimo parinktys. Įrankių juostos mygtukai yra "
"dinamiški, o tai reiškia, kad jų būsena (įjungta arba išjungta) priklauso "
"nuo skirtingų veiksnių."

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.p:389-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"def\">The status bar:</span> The status bar is shown in the "
"bottom, and contains several useful options and features."
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"def\">Būsenos juosta:</span> Būsenos juosta rodoma apačioje ir "
"joje yra keletas naudingų parinkčių bei funkcijų."

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.img[alt]:390-29
msgid ""
"Status bar showing page number, word count, insert mode, selection mode, "
"language, edit mode, navigation, zoom, and search"
msgstr ""
"Būsenos juostoje rodomas puslapio numeris, žodžių skaičius, įterpimo "
"režimas, pasirinkimo režimas, kalba, redagavimo režimas, naršymas, mastelio "
"keitimas ir paieška"

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.p:393-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"def\">The search bar:</span> Searching starts automatically "
"when content is inserted in the search box, and the document window "
"automatically moves to the first occurrence found. Searching is not case-"
"sensitive. There are three buttons right next to the search box:"
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"def\">Paieškos juosta:</span> Paieška pradedama automatiškai, "
"kai į paieškos laukelį įterpiamas turinys, o dokumento langas automatiškai "
"perkeliamas į pirmą rastą įrašą. Paieška neskiria didžiųjų ir mažųjų "
"raidžių. Šalia paieškos laukelio yra trys mygtukai:"

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.ul.li:395-7
msgid "Search backwards"
msgstr "Atbulinė paieška"

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.ul.li:396-7
msgid "Search forward"
msgstr "Ieškoti pirmyn"

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.ul.li:397-7
msgid "Cancel the search (appears only when a text has been searched)"
msgstr "Atšaukti paiešką (rodomas tik esant teksto paieškai)"

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.p:401-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"def\">The zoom bar:</span> The zoom bar includes buttons to "
"reset zoom to 100%, zoom out and zoom in. The zoom applies to the document "
"area, the user interface is not affected. The current level of zoom is shown "
"in this area."
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"def\">Mastelio keitimo juosta:</span> Mastelio keitimo "
"juostoje yra mygtukai, skirti atkurti 100 % mastelį, atitolinti ir "
"priartinti vaizdą. Mastelio keitimas taikomas dokumento sričiai, vartotojo "
"sąsajos tai nepaveikia. Dabartinis mastelio lygis rodomas šioje srityje."

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.p:402-5
msgid ""
"Text, charts, shapes and svg images will stay sharp, when zooming in, you "
"will only see pixels appear at inserted images, such as jpg’s or png’s."
msgstr ""
"Tekstas, diagramos, formos ir svg vaizdai išliks ryškūs; priartinus matysite "
"pikselius tik įterptuose vaizduose, pvz., 'jpg' arba 'png'."

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.p:403-5
msgid "Using the browser zoom affects the document and user interface areas."
msgstr ""
"Naršyklės mastelio keitimo naudojimas paveikia dokumento ir vartotojo "
"sąsajos sritis."

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.p:406-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"def\">The information bar:</span> The information bar displays "
"details about the current document. The actual information depends on the "
"nature of the document."
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"def\">Informacijos juosta:</span> Informacijos juostoje rodoma "
"išsami informacija apie dabartinį dokumentą. Tikroji informacija priklauso "
"nuo dokumento pobūdžio."

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.img[alt]:407-29
msgid ""
"Information bar showing page navigation arrows, zoom controls, and zoom level"
msgstr ""
"Informacijos juosta, kurioje rodomos puslapio naršymo rodyklės, mastelio "
"keitimo valdikliai ir mastelio lygis"

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.p:412-5
msgid ""
"Your documents are stored and managed in the cloud storage that is "
"integrated with <span class=\"productname\">{productname}</span>."
msgstr ""
"Jūsų dokumentai saugomi ir tvarkomi debesies saugykloje, kuri integruota su "
"<span class=\"productname\">{productname}</span>."

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.p:413-30
msgid ""
"To download a document download it from the <span class=\"productname\""
">{productname}</span> application’s <span class=\"ui\">File</span> menu. The "
"download formats available depends on the application. All applications "
"exports documents in PDF format."
msgstr ""
"Norėdami atsisiųsti dokumentą, atsisiųskite jį iš programos <span class="
"\"productname\">{productname}</span> meniu <span class=\"ui\">Failas</span>. "
"Galimi atsisiuntimo formatai priklauso nuo programos. Visos programos "
"eksportuoja dokumentus PDF formatu."

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.p:414-30
msgid ""
"To open document, click on the file to open the <span class=\"productname\""
">{productname}</span> module associated to the document format."
msgstr ""
"Norėdami atidaryti dokumentą, spustelėkite failą, kad atidarytumėte su "
"dokumento formatu susietą programos <span class=\"productname\""
">{productname}</span> modulį."

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.p:415-30
msgid ""
"Documents in <span class=\"productname\">{productname}</span> save "
"automatically, but if you are concerned that a document is synchronized as "
"quickly as possible you can also force saving using the <span class=\"ui\""
">File</span> menu’s <span class=\"ui\">Save</span> entry."
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"productname\">{productname}</span> dokumentai išsaugomi "
"automatiškai, bet jei norite, kad dokumentas būtų sinchronizuojamas "
"anksčiau, galite priverstinai išsaugoti naudodami meniu <span class=\"ui\""
">Failas</span> opcija <span class=\"ui\">Išsaugoti</span>."

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.p:416-30
msgid ""
"Depending on the capabilities of your browser, the print window may appear "
"or a “Download PDF export?” popup appears. You can print this PDF in your "
"favorite PDF reader."
msgstr ""
"Priklausomai nuo jūsų naršyklės galimybių, gali pasirodyti spausdinimo "
"langas arba iššokantis langas „Atsisiųsti eksportuotą PDF?“. Šį PDF failą "
"galite atsispausdinti mėgiama PDF programa."

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.p:417-30
msgid ""
"When closing a document, it is automatically saved if it has been changed."
msgstr "Uždarius dokumentą, jis automatiškai išsaugomas, jei buvo pakeitimų."

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.p:421-5
msgid ""
"Document editing should be familiar to everyone that has used an office "
"application before, but here are some distinctive features:"
msgstr ""
"Dokumentų redagavimas turėtų būti pažįstamas visiems, kurie anksčiau "
"naudojosi „Office“ programomis, tačiau čia yra keletas išskirtinių savybių:"

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.h4:423-5
msgid "Copy and Paste"
msgstr "Kopijuoti ir įklijuoti"

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.p:424-5
msgid ""
"Rich content copy/cut and paste is supported, not only within a given "
"document, but also across documents on the same or different <span class="
"\"productname\">{productname}</span>. For these internal uses, users can "
"copy/cut content, including images and mixed content, on PC by using the "
"keyboard shortcuts directly (<kbd>Ctrl</kbd><span class=\"kbd--plus\" aria-"
"hidden=\"true\">+</span><kbd>X</kbd>, <kbd>Ctrl</kbd><span class=\"kbd--"
"plus\" aria-hidden=\"true\">+</span><kbd>C</kbd>, <kbd>Ctrl</kbd><span class="
"\"kbd--plus\" aria-hidden=\"true\">+</span><kbd>V</kbd>). For security "
"reasons it is necessary to use <kbd>Ctrl</kbd><span class=\"kbd--plus\" aria-"
"hidden=\"true\">+</span><kbd>V</kbd> to paste on PC, but context menus can "
"be used for cut and copy. On Android or iOS selecting text by double "
"tapping, and using a long-tap to access copy/cut/paste via the context menu "
"is required."
msgstr ""
"Palaikomas raiškiojo turinio kopijavimas / iškirpimas ir įklijavimas ne tik "
"konkrečiame dokumente, bet ir tarp dokumentų tame pačiame ar skirtinguose "
"<span class=\"productname\">{productname}</span>. Šiems vidiniams tikslams "
"vartotojai gali kopijuoti / iškirpti turinį, įskaitant vaizdus ir mišrų "
"turinį, kompiuteryje tiesiogiai naudodami sparčiuosius klavišus (<kbd>Ctrl</"
"kbd><span class=\"kbd--plus\" aria-hidden=\"true\">+</span><kbd>X</kbd>, "
"<kbd>Ctrl</kbd><span class=\"kbd--plus\" aria-hidden=\"true\""
">+</span><kbd>C</kbd>, <kbd>Ctrl</kbd><span class=\"kbd--plus\" aria-hidden="
"\"true\">+</span><kbd>V</kbd>). Dėl saugumo priežasčių norint įklijuoti "
"kompiuteryje, būtina naudoti <kbd>Ctrl</kbd><span class=\"kbd--plus\" aria-"
"hidden=\"true\">+</span><kbd>V</kbd>, tačiau iškirpimui ir kopijavimui "
"galima naudoti kontekstinius meniu. „Android“ arba „iOS“ sistemose tekstą "
"reikia pasirinkti dukart spustelėjus, o norint pasiekti kopijavimo / "
"iškirpimo / įklijavimo funkcijas per kontekstinį meniu, reikia ilgiau "
"palaikyti paspaudus."

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.p:425-5
msgid ""
"To copy larger pieces of content to other applications on your device, users "
"need to press the <span class=\"ui\">Start download</span> button, and then "
"re-copy this to their clipboard in order to make it available to the target "
"application to read. This is possible via a tiny widget that pops up in the "
"bottom-right corner, and is only necessary to export the content for pasting "
"in external applications. This step also converts complex object types into "
"static images."
msgstr ""
"Norėdami nukopijuoti didesnius turinio fragmentus į kitas įrenginio "
"programas, vartotojai turi paspausti mygtuką <span class=\"ui\">Pradėti "
"atsisiuntimą</span> ir dar kartą nukopijuoti šį failą į iškarpinę, kad "
"tikslinė programa galėtų jį perskaityti. Tai įmanoma naudojant mažytį "
"valdiklį, kuris iššoka apatiniame dešiniajame kampe, ir jis reikalingas tik "
"norint eksportuoti turinį įklijavimui į išorines programas. Šis veiksmas "
"taip pat konvertuoja sudėtingus objektų tipus į statinius vaizdus."

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.h4:428-5
msgid "Document repair"
msgstr "Dokumento taisymas"

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.p:429-5
msgid ""
"When multiple people edit the same document concurrently, it is possible for "
"their changes to conflict and this can cause some confusion. The Document "
"Repair function allows users to undo other editor’s changes to the document "
"to a previous state."
msgstr ""
"Kai keli žmonės vienu metu redaguoja tą patį dokumentą, jų atlikti "
"pakeitimai gali konfliktuoti ir sukelti painiavą. Dokumento taisymo funkcija "
"leidžia vartotojams anuliuoti kitų redaktorių atliktus dokumento pakeitimus "
"iki ankstesnės būsenos."

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.p:430-5
msgid ""
"To jump back to the selected state, select it with the mouse and hit <span "
"class=\"ui\">Jump to state</span>."
msgstr ""
"Norėdami grįžti į pasirinktą būseną, pasirinkite ją pele ir paspauskite "
"<span class=\"ui\">Pereiti į būseną</span>."

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.img[alt]:431-29
msgid ""
"Repair Document dialog listing past document states with columns for action "
"type, author, and timestamp"
msgstr ""
"Dokumento taisymo dialogo langas, kuriame pateikiamos ankstesnės dokumento "
"būsenos su veiksmo tipo, autoriaus ir laiko žymos stulpeliais"

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.p:432-5
msgid ""
"This is particularly useful – say when a colleague inadvertently selected "
"all text in the document with <kbd>Ctrl</kbd><span class=\"kbd--plus\" aria-"
"hidden=\"true\">+</span><kbd>A</kbd> and proceeded to type over it "
"destroying it – while you were concurrently editing."
msgstr ""
"Tai ypač naudinga, pavyzdžiui, kai kolega netyčia pažymėjo visą dokumento "
"tekstą naudodamas <kbd>Ctrl</kbd><span class=\"kbd--plus\" aria-hidden=\"true"
"\">+</span><kbd>A</kbd> ir jį perrašė, kol jūs tuo metu jį redagavote."

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.h4:435-5
msgid "Inactive document"
msgstr "Neaktyvus dokumentas"

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.p:436-5
msgid ""
"When <span class=\"productname\">{productname}</span> detects that there has "
"not been any activity in the browser for a while, it puts the document in an "
"“Inactive” state. The document is shown with a transparent gray overlay, "
"with the message “Inactive document – please click to resume editing”."
msgstr ""
"Kai <span class=\"productname\">{productname}</span> aptinka, kad naršyklėje "
"kurį laiką nebuvo vykdoma jokia veikla, dokumentas perkeliamas į „Neaktyvią“ "
"būseną. Dokumentas rodomas su permatomu pilku perdengimu ir pranešimu „"
"Neaktyvus dokumentas – spustelėkite, jei norite tęsti redagavimą“."

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.img[alt]:437-29
msgid ""
"Idle document overlay with the message: Idle document - please click to "
"reload and resume editing"
msgstr ""
"Neaktyvaus dokumento langas su pranešimu: Neaktyvus dokumentas – "
"spustelėkite, kad įkeltumėte iš naujo ir tęstumėte redagavimą"

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.p:438-5
msgid ""
"To continue editing, click on the document and the layover and message "
"disappear. Any changes that may have been made by other users – while "
"collaboratively editing the document – are re-loaded."
msgstr ""
"Norėdami tęsti redagavimą, spustelėkite dokumentą ir perdengimas bei "
"pranešimas išnyks. Visi pakeitimai, kuriuos galėjo atlikti kiti vartotojai "
"bendrai redaguodami dokumentą, bus atnaujinti."

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.h4:441-5
msgid "Pasting"
msgstr "Įklijavimas"

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.p:442-5
msgid ""
"When you paste content copied from within the same document, the format and "
"elements are maintained. If you copy from another document, in another tab "
"or browser window, or from outside of the browser, the pasted content will "
"preserve rich text."
msgstr ""
"Įklijavus iš to paties dokumento nukopijuotą turinį, formatas ir elementai "
"išsaugomi. Jei kopijuojate iš kito dokumento, kito skirtuko ar naršyklės "
"lango arba ne iš naršyklės, įklijuotame turinyje išsaugomas raiškusis "
"tekstas."

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.p:443-5
msgid ""
"You can paste as unformatted text with the keyboard shortcut: <kbd>Ctrl</"
"kbd><span class=\"kbd--plus\" aria-hidden=\"true\">+</span><kbd>Shift</"
"kbd><span class=\"kbd--plus\" aria-hidden=\"true\">+</span><kbd>V</kbd>"
msgstr ""
"Galite įklijuoti kaip neformatuotą tekstą naudodami sparčiuosius klavišus: "
"<kbd>Ctrl</kbd><span class=\"kbd--plus\" aria-hidden=\"true\""
">+</span><kbd>Shift</kbd><span class=\"kbd--plus\" aria-hidden=\"true\""
">+</span><kbd>V</kbd>"

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.p:444-5
msgid ""
"When you paste text from within the document, formatting will be respected. "
"You can also paste objects, such as images, if they are copied from the "
"document you are working in."
msgstr ""
"Įklijavus tekstą iš dokumento, bus laikomasi formatavimo. Taip pat galite "
"įklijuoti objektus, pvz., paveikslėlius, jei jie nukopijuoti iš dokumento, "
"kuriame dirbate."

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.p:445-5
msgid ""
"When you paste text from outside of the document (another browser window or "
"a desktop application), it will be pasted as rich text."
msgstr ""
"Kai įklijuosite tekstą iš už dokumento ribų (kito naršyklės lango arba "
"darbalaukio programos), jis bus įklijuotas raiškiojo teksto formatu."

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.p:446-5
msgid ""
"When you have internal cut or copied content, you can paste this content "
"using the context menu."
msgstr ""
"Kai turite vidinį iškirptą arba nukopijuotą turinį, galite jį įklijuoti "
"naudodami kontekstinį meniu."

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.h4:452-5
msgid "Adding charts"
msgstr "Diagramų pridėjimas"

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.p:453-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"productname\">{productname}</span> supports inserting and "
"visualization of charts in documents. To add a chart:"
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"productname\">{productname}</span> palaiko diagramų įterpimą "
"ir vizualizavimą dokumentuose. Norėdami pridėti diagramą:"

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.ol.li:455-7
msgid ""
"Select a table in text document, a range in a spreadsheet or a table in a "
"presentation."
msgstr ""
"Pasirinkite lentelę tekstiniame dokumente, diapazoną skaičiuoklėje arba "
"lentelę prezentacijoje."

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.ol.li:456-7
msgid ""
"Choose <span class=\"ui\">Insert</span> → <span class=\"ui\">Charts</span>. "
"Customize your chart on the sidebar:"
msgstr ""
"Pasirinkite <span class=\"ui\">Įterpti</span> → <span class=\"ui\">"
"Diagramos</span>. Diagramą tinkinkite šoninėje juostoje:"

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.ol.div.img[alt]:459-31
msgid ""
"Chart Wizard dialog with chart type list on the left, chart style previews, "
"3D and shape options"
msgstr ""
"Diagramos vedlio dialogo langas su diagramos tipų sąrašu kairėje, diagramos "
"stilių peržiūromis, 3D ir formos parinktimis"

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.ol.li:460-7
msgid "If no table or range was selected, a prototype chart is displayed."
msgstr ""
"Jei nepasirinkta jokia lentelė ar diapazonas, rodoma prototipinė diagrama."

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.img[alt]:462-29
msgid ""
"Column chart with grouped bars showing data for four rows across three "
"columns"
msgstr ""
"Stulpelių diagrama su sugrupuotomis juostomis rodo keturių eilučių duomenis "
"trijuose stulpeliuose"

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.p:464-28
msgid ""
"<span class=\"def\">Chart editing:</span> Double click the chart to select. "
"Use context menus to add chart elements such as title, axis, and other. "
"Choose <span class=\"ui\">Data Range</span> and <span class=\"ui\">Chart "
"Type</span> to edit chart data and select chart type."
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"def\">Diagramos redagavimas:</span> Dukart spustelėkite "
"diagramą, kad ją pasirinktumėte. Norėdami pridėti diagramos elementus, pvz., "
"pavadinimą, ašį ir kt., naudokite kontekstinius meniu. Pasirinkite <span "
"class=\"ui\">Duomenų diapazonas</span> ir <span class=\"ui\">Diagramos "
"tipas</span>, kad redaguotumėte diagramos duomenis ir pasirinktumėte "
"diagramos tipą."

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.p:465-28
msgid ""
"<span class=\"def\">Chart formatting:</span> The same context menu brings "
"you to chart data table and chart type selection."
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"def\">Diagramos formatavimas:</span> Tas pats kontekstinis "
"meniu nukreipia jus į diagramos duomenų lentelę ir diagramos tipo "
"pasirinkimą."

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.p:466-28
msgid ""
"<span class=\"def\">Data series formatting:</span> Open the context menu and "
"choose <span class=\"ui\">Format data series</span>."
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"def\">Duomenų sekų formatavimas:</span> Atidarykite "
"kontekstinį meniu ir pasirinkite <span class=\"ui\">Formatuoti duomenų seką</"
"span>."

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.h4:468-5
msgid "Handling images"
msgstr "Paveikslėlių tvarkymas"

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.p:469-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"productname\">{productname}</span> inserts images in the text "
"document from your local computer or from your cloud storage. Inserted "
"images are always embedded in the document."
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"productname\">{productname}</span> į tekstinį dokumentą "
"įterpia vaizdus iš jūsų vietinio kompiuterio arba debesies saugyklos. "
"Įterpti vaizdai visada įdedami į dokumentą."

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.p:470-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"def\">Insert image:</span> Clicking on the <span class=\"ui\""
">Insert image</span> icon allows you to choose an image from the cloud "
"storage's folders and shares."
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"def\">Įterpti paveikslėlį:</span> Spustelėję piktogramą <span "
"class=\"ui\">Įterpti paveikslėlį</span>, leidžia pasirinkti paveikslėlį iš "
"debesies saugyklos aplankų ir bendrinamų elementų."

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.p:471-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"def\">Insert local image:</span> opens the browser file picker "
"to upload the image from your local computer and insert it into the document."
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"def\">Įterpti vietinį vaizdą:</span> atidaro failų naršyklės "
"dialogą, kad būtų galima įkelti vaizdą iš vietinio kompiuterio ir įterpti jį "
"į dokumentą."

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.p:472-5
msgid ""
"Images can be resized, rotated and anchored. Text can be wrapped around the "
"image. Select the image and open the context menu. Use the images handles to "
"resize the image with the mouse."
msgstr ""
"Vaizdų dydį galima keisti, pasukti ir pritvirtinti. Tekstą galima apvynioti "
"aplink vaizdą. Pasirinkite vaizdą ir atidarykite kontekstinį meniu. Norėdami "
"pakeisti vaizdo dydį pele, naudokite vaizdo rankenėles."

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.h4:475-5
msgid "Comments in documents"
msgstr "Komentarai dokumentuose"

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.p:476-5
msgid ""
"Insert comments in <span class=\"productname\">{productname}</span> in "
"places that need special reader attention. Comments are displayed on the "
"right and carry the name and date of the issuer."
msgstr ""
"Įterpkite komentarus į <span class=\"productname\">{productname}</span> "
"vietas, kurioms reikia ypatingo skaitytojo dėmesio. Komentarai rodomi "
"dešinėje ir juose nurodomas autoriaus vardas ir data."

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.img[alt]:477-29
msgid ""
"Comment box showing author name, date, and the comment text, displayed "
"beside the document"
msgstr ""
"Komentarų laukelis, kuriame rodomas autoriaus vardas, data ir komentaro "
"tekstas, rodomas šalia dokumento"

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.p:478-5
msgid ""
"Click on the submenu (<span class=\"cool-annotation-menu icon-size\"></span>)"
" icon to reply, move and delete comments."
msgstr ""
"Norėdami atsakyti, perkelti arba ištrinti komentarus, spustelėkite submeniu "
"(<span class=\"cool-annotation-menu icon-size\"></span>) piktogramą."

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.h4:481-5
msgid "Spellchecking"
msgstr "Rašybos tikrinimas"

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.p:482-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"productname\">{productname}</span> can check spelling in text "
"documents, spreadsheets and presentations. A red wavy underline indicates "
"misspelled words. Click on the right mouse button to open a context menu "
"with suggested misspelling corrections."
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.img[alt]:483-29
msgid "Text with a red wavy underline beneath a misspelled word"
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.p:484-5
msgid ""
"To systematically spell-check the whole document use the <span class=\"ui\""
">Tools</span> menu’s <span class=\"ui\">Spelling</span> option."
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.p:491-30
msgid ""
"You edit an online spreadsheet in the same way you edit a desktop "
"spreadsheet. Operations like entering data, selecting ranges, columns, rows "
"or sheets are the same. Use the keyboard, menus or toolbar to command "
"actions in the spreadsheet. Dragging cells contents to fill cells with data "
"is also supported. Copy, cut and paste commands are available from the "
"context menu. Following entered data with a <kbd>Tab</kbd> will move the "
"cursor to the next cell to the right, and with an <kbd>Enter</kbd> to the "
"cell below for easy further data entry."
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.p:496-5
msgid ""
"Formulas are entered in the formula bar. Enter '=' and insert the formula."
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.p:497-5
msgid "All spreadsheets functions and mathematical rules applies."
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.div.img[alt]:498-29
msgid ""
"Formula bar showing cell reference B1, function wizard icon, and the formula "
"=SIN(PI()*A1/10)"
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.p:499-5
msgid ""
"The formula language should be extremely familiar to any spreadsheet user, "
"and is specified in great detail in the <a href=\"https://www.oasis-open.org/"
"committees/download.php/16826/openformula-spec-20060221.html\" target="
"\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">OASIS OpenFormula specification</a>."
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.p:505-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"def\">Direct formatting:</span> You can format spreadsheet "
"cells, columns, rows and sheets by formatting directly from the menus, "
"toolbar or context menus. Direct formatting applies only to the current "
"object selected. To format a cell either use the menu or hit <kbd>Ctrl</"
"kbd><span class=\"kbd--plus\" aria-hidden=\"true\">+</span><kbd>1</kbd>. The "
"dialog allows complex and custom number formatting, as well as font, complex "
"border, background, cell protection and other options."
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.div.img[alt]:506-29
msgid ""
"Format Cells dialog on the Numbers tab with category list, format options, "
"decimal places, and format code"
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.p:511-30
msgid ""
"<span class=\"def\">Sorting data:</span> You can sort a list of numbers or "
"text ascending or descending. <span class=\"productname\">{productname}</"
"span> automatically detects cells that are headers, and adjoining columns, "
"to extend the selection."
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.p:512-30
msgid ""
"<span class=\"def\">Filtering data:</span> Filters and advanced filters "
"allow you to work on certain filtered rows (records) of a data range. In the "
"spreadsheets in <span class=\"productname\">{productname}</span> there are "
"various possibilities for applying filters."
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.ol.li:514-7
msgid ""
"One use for the <span class=\"ui\">AutoFilter</span> function is to quickly "
"restrict the display to records with identical entries in a data field."
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.ol.li.div.img[alt]:516-34
msgid ""
"AutoFilter dropdown menu on a spreadsheet column with sort, filter by color, "
"filter by condition, and checkboxes for individual values"
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.ol.li:518-7
msgid ""
"In the <span class=\"ui\">Standard Filter</span> dialog, you can also define "
"ranges which contain the values in particular data fields. You can use the "
"standard filter to connect the conditions with either a logical AND or a "
"logical OR operator."
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.ol.li:519-7
msgid ""
"The <span class=\"ui\">Advanced Filter</span> allows up to a total of eight "
"filter conditions. With advanced filters you enter the conditions directly "
"into the sheet."
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.p:523-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"def\">Outlining:</span> You can create an outline of your data "
"and group rows and columns together so that you can collapse and expand the "
"groups with a single click making it easy to represent hierarchical data."
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.div.img[alt]:524-29
msgid ""
"Spreadsheet with row and column grouping controls showing outline level "
"buttons and collapse/expand toggles"
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.p:527-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"def\">Data validation:</span> For each cell, you can define "
"entries to be valid. Invalid entries to a cell will be rejected. To enable "
"data validation:"
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.ol.li:529-7
msgid ""
"Choose <span class=\"ui\">Validity</span> from the <span class=\"ui\">Data</"
"span> menu. The <span class=\"ui\">Validity</span> dialog opens."
msgstr ""
"Meniu <span class=\"ui\">Duomenys</span> pasirinkite <span class=\"ui\">"
"Galiojimas</span>. Atsidarys dialogo langas <span class=\"ui\">Galiojimas</"
"span>."

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.ol.div.img[alt]:532-31
msgid ""
"Validity dialog on the Criteria tab with Allow set to List, showing options "
"for empty cells, selection list, and entry values"
msgstr ""
"\"Galiojimas\" dialogo langas skirtuke „Kriterijai“, kai „Leisti“ nustatyta "
"kaip „Sąrašas“, rodo tuščių langelių, pasirinkimo sąrašo ir įvesties "
"reikšmių parinktis"

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.ol.li:533-7
msgid ""
"Select the validity criterion in the <span class=\"ui\">Allow</span> drop-"
"box list. Depending on the criterion, more options show. Fill the required "
"data."
msgstr ""
"Išskleidžiamajame sąraše <span class=\"ui\">Leisti</span> pasirinkite "
"galiojimo kriterijų. Priklausomai nuo kriterijaus, rodoma daugiau parinkčių. "
"Užpildykite reikiamus duomenis."

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.ol.li:534-7
msgid ""
"Use the <span class=\"ui\">Input Help</span> and <span class=\"ui\">Error "
"Alert</span> tabs to enhance the user interactions. Click <span class=\"ui\""
">OK</span> to close the dialog."
msgstr ""
"Norėdami pagerinti naudotojų sąveiką, naudokite skirtukus <span class=\"ui\">"
"Įvesties pagalba</span> ir <span class=\"ui\">Klaidos įspėjimas</span>. "
"Spustelėkite <span class=\"ui\">Gerai</span>, kad uždarytumėte dialogo langą."

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.ol.div.img[alt]:537-31
msgid ""
"Cell dropdown list showing validated entries such as Apple, Pear, Banana, "
"Kiwi, and Lemon"
msgstr ""
"Langelių išskleidžiamasis sąrašas, kuriame rodomi patvirtinti įrašai, pvz., „"
"Obuolys“, „Kriaušė“, „Bananas“, „Kivis“ ir „Citrina“"

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.ol.li:538-7
msgid ""
"To remove the validity of the cell, open the dialog and set the <span class="
"\"ui\">Allow</span> list to “All values”."
msgstr ""
"Norėdami pašalinti langelio galiojimą, atidarykite dialogo langą ir "
"nustatykite <span class=\"ui\">Leisti</span> sąrašą į „Visos reikšmės“."

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.p:542-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"def\">Comments:</span> In a spreadsheet you can insert one "
"comment per cell. When you select <span class=\"ui\">Insert comment</span>, "
"a popup appears that allows you to write the content for the comment. A red "
"dot shows on the top right corner of the cell when it has a comment. Hover "
"the mouse on the cell to display comments."
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"def\">Komentarai:</span> Skaičiuoklėje galite įterpti po vieną "
"komentarą į kiekvieną langelį. Pasirinkus <span class=\"ui\">Įterpti "
"komentarą</span>, pasirodys iššokantis langas, kuriame galėsite parašyti "
"komentarą. Jei langelyje yra komentaras, viršutiniame dešiniajame kampe bus "
"rodomas raudonas taškas. Užveskite pelės žymeklį ant langelio, kad būtų "
"rodomi komentarai."

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.div.img[alt]:543-29
msgid ""
"Spreadsheet cell with a comment popup showing the author, date, comment "
"text, and Save/Cancel buttons"
msgstr ""
"Skaičiuoklės langelis su iššokančiu komentaro langu, kuriame rodomas "
"autorius, data, komentaro tekstas ir mygtukai „Įrašyti / Atšaukti“"

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.p:546-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"def\">Conditional formatting:</span> <span class=\"productname"
"\">{productname}</span> adds symbols to each cell of a range based on cells "
"conditions. Select the cell range and click the <span class=\"ui\""
">Conditional Formatting</span> icon on the toolbar. Select the symbol set to "
"apply on the range."
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"def\">Sąlyginis formatavimas:</span> <span "
"class=\"productname\">{productname}</span> į kiekvieną diapazono langelį "
"įtraukia simbolius pagal langelių sąlygas. Pasirinkite langelių diapazoną ir "
"įrankių juostoje spustelėkite piktogramą <span class=\"ui\">Sąlyginis "
"formatavimas</span>. Pasirinkite simbolių rinkinį, kurį norite taikyti "
"diapazone."

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.div.img[alt]:547-29
msgid ""
"Conditional formatting icon set picker showing arrows, circles, traffic "
"lights, stars, smiley faces, and bar chart symbol sets"
msgstr ""
"Sąlyginio formatavimo piktogramų rinkinio parinkiklis rodantis rodykles, "
"apskritimus, šviesoforus, žvaigždes, besišypsančius veidus ir juostinės "
"diagramos simbolių rinkinius"

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.p:555-30
msgid ""
"<span class=\"productname\">{productname}</span> edits text documents in the "
"same way you edit a desktop document. It provides a What You See Is What You "
"Get (WYSIWYG) layout – that conveniently lays out the document as it will be "
"printed. Operations like typing text, cut, copy and pasting contents, "
"selecting text, inserting, resizing, anchoring images, adding and handling "
"tables and charts, are similar to a desktop word processor. Use the "
"keyboard, menus and toolbars to interact with your document."
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"productname\">{productname}</span> redaguoja tekstinius "
"dokumentus taip pat, kaip redaguojate darbalaukio dokumentą. Jis pateikia „"
"Ką matote, tą ir gaunate“ (WYSIWYG) išdėstymą, kuris patogiai išdėsto "
"dokumentą taip, kaip jis bus spausdinamas. Tokios operacijos kaip teksto "
"rašymas, iškirpimas, kopijavimas ir įklijavimas, teksto pasirinkimas, "
"įterpimas, dydžio keitimas, vaizdų įtvirtinimas, lentelių ir diagramų "
"pridėjimas ir tvarkymas yra panašios į kompiuterio teksto redaktoriaus. "
"Norėdami sąveikauti su dokumentu, naudokite klaviatūrą, meniu ir įrankių "
"juostas."

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.p:559-30
msgid ""
"Context menus are available on clicking the right mouse button. The commands "
"available in the context menu are related - not extensively - to the "
"underlying object in the document."
msgstr ""
"Kontekstiniai meniu pasiekiami spustelėjus dešinįjį pelės mygtuką. "
"Kontekstinio meniu komandos yra susijusios (ne pilnai) su dokumente esančiu "
"objektu."

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.h3:562-5
msgid "Formatting text"
msgstr "Teksto Formatavimas"

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.p:564-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"productname\">{productname}</span> supports modern techniques "
"for paragraph formatting through styles. A style is a set of text properties "
"(font, color, background and many more) labeled with a name, the style name. "
"Use a style to apply the same set of properties to many paragraphs in the "
"document and produce a uniform, professional look. Also, if you change one "
"of the style formatting properties, all paragraphs with the same style "
"change formatting as well, simplifying the effort of formatting many "
"paragraphs individually."
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"productname\">{productname}</span> palaiko modernias pastraipų "
"formatavimo technikas naudojant stilius. Stilius yra teksto ypatybių "
"(šrifto, spalvos, fono ir daugelio kitų) rinkinys, pažymėtas pavadinimu – "
"stiliaus pavadinimu. Naudokite stilių, kad tą patį ypatybių rinkinį "
"pritaikytumėte daugeliui dokumento pastraipų ir sukurtumėte vienodą, "
"profesionalų vaizdą. Be to, jei pakeisite vieną iš stiliaus formatavimo "
"ypatybių, visų to paties stiliaus pastraipų formatavimas taip pat pasikeis, "
"todėl bus lengviau formatuoti daugelį pastraipų atskirai."

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.p:565-5
msgid ""
"In contrast, direct formatting applies formatting to selected excerpts of "
"the document contents. On a long document, direct formatting must be applied "
"in every text excerpt, turning text formatting a long task, subject to "
"errors and delays."
msgstr ""
"Priešingai, tiesioginis formatavimas taiko formatavimą pasirinktoms "
"dokumento dalims. Ilgame dokumente tiesioginis formatavimas turi būti "
"taikomas kiekvienai teksto daliai, todėl teksto formatavimas tampa ilga "
"užduotimi, kurioje gali pasitaikyti klaidų ir vėlavimų."

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.p:567-30
msgid ""
"<span class=\"def\">Direct formatting:</span> You can format text document "
"objects by formatting directly from the menus, toolbar or context menus. "
"Direct formatting applies only to the current object selected."
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.p:569-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"def\">Style formatting:</span> <span class=\"productname\""
">{productname}</span> supports paragraph styles. You can apply an existing "
"paragraph style to a paragraph. Choose menu <span class=\"ui\">Edit</span> → "
"<span class=\"ui\">Edit styles</span> to change style."
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.div.img[alt]:570-29
msgid ""
"Paragraph dialog on the Indents and Spacing tab with settings for indent, "
"spacing, and line spacing, and a preview on the right"
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.h4:576-5
msgid "Handling Tables"
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.p:577-5
msgid ""
"Insert tables with proper icon in the toolbar. Select the initial number of "
"rows and columns. Add rows and columns with the cell context menu. Merge "
"cells with the <span class=\"ui\">Table</span> menu. The default paragraph "
"style inside cells is “Table contents”."
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.div.img[alt]:578-29
msgid ""
"Insert Table picker showing a grid to select the number of rows and columns, "
"currently showing 5 by 3"
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.p:581-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"def\">Formatting cells:</span> Click in the cell or range of "
"cells and choose menu <span class=\"ui\">Table</span> → <span class=\"ui\""
">Properties</span>. Fine tune the table with the properties dialog."
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.h4:584-5
msgid "Track changes"
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.p:585-5
msgid ""
"When you turn on Track Changes, <span class=\"productname\">{productname}</"
"span> marks up new changes made to the document. Select this option again to "
"turn it off."
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.div.img[alt]:586-29
#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.div.img[alt]:713-29
msgid ""
"Tracked change shown as a comment box beside the document with author name, "
"date, and change description"
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.p:587-5
msgid ""
"Changes made by different people are shown in different colors and each "
"tracked change can be accepted or rejected, using the box that appears on "
"the right. You can also add a comment there."
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.h4:590-5
msgid "Other advanced features"
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.p:591-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"def\">Comments:</span> Comments are inserted in the text and "
"displayed on the right side of the screen."
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.p:592-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"def\">Formatting marks:</span> Paragraph, page and unbreakable "
"spaces are shown as marks to assist text alignment, editing and formatting."
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.p:593-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"def\">Fields:</span> A basic set of fields is available to "
"insert in the document."
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.p:594-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"def\">Alphabetical index:</span> Existing alphabetical index "
"can be updated with new entries."
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.p:595-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"def\">Page header and footer:</span> Headers and footers are "
"available for the existing page style applied in the document at the cursor "
"position."
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.p:596-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"def\">Footnotes and endnotes:</span> Footnotes and endnotes "
"are supported."
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.p:604-30
msgid ""
"<span class=\"productname\">{productname}</span> Impress edits presentations "
"in a way that should be familiar to people. Operations like typing text, "
"cut, copy and pasting contents, selecting text, inserting, resizing, "
"anchoring images, adding and handling tables, are similar to a desktop "
"presentation application. Use the keyboard, menus and toolbars to perform "
"actions in your document."
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.p:609-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"productname\">{productname}</span> displays presentation slide "
"shows, including a subset of slide transitions and object animations. Choose "
"the slide show from the menu or click on the icon in the bottom left toolbar "
"in the slide pane."
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.p:610-5
msgid ""
"To exit a <span class=\"productname\">{productname}</span> slide show, press "
"the <kbd>Esc</kbd> key to return to the presentation edit mode."
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.p:616-5
msgid ""
"Click on any slide thumbnail in the pane to switch to this slide to view or "
"edit it."
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.p:617-5
msgid ""
"Use the slide pane toolbar in the bottom to start the slideshow, add slide, "
"duplicate or delete the current slide."
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.p:623-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"def\">Slide layouts:</span> <span class=\"productname\""
">{productname}</span> Impress lets you change the slide layout. Select the "
"desired slide layout in the drop-down layout list."
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.div.img[alt]:624-29
msgid ""
"Slide properties panel showing format, orientation, background, and master "
"slide settings, with a layout gallery of thumbnail options below"
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.p:626-30
msgid ""
"<span class=\"def\">Master slide:</span> Select the master slide associated "
"to the current slide. Format and arrange slide elements in the master slide."
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.p:627-30
msgid ""
"<span class=\"def\">Slide transitions:</span> <span class=\"productname\""
">{productname}</span> Impress provides visual effects when displaying a new "
"slide in the slide show. Slide transitions are property of the slide, use "
"the side bar to set the slide transition when in edit mode."
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.p:628-30
msgid ""
"<span class=\"def\">Object animation:</span> Individual objects in the slide "
"can have animations. Use the side bar to configure the slide transition for "
"a selected object or set of objects."
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.p:629-30
msgid ""
"<span class=\"def\">Tables:</span> Insert tables in the presentation. Use "
"the sidebar to select the table theme."
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.h4:635-5
msgid ""
"What are the document file formats supported by <span class=\"productname\""
">{productname}</span>?"
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.p:636-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"productname\">{productname}</span> supports both reading and "
"writing for the following file formats:"
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.ul.li:638-7
msgid ""
"Text documents: Microsoft formats DOC, DOCX, RTF. OpenDocument Format ODT"
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.ul.li:639-7
msgid "Spreadsheets: Microsoft formats XLS, XLSX, OpenDocument Format ODS"
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.ul.li:640-7
msgid "Presentations: Microsoft formats PPT, PPTX, OpenDocument Format ODP"
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.h4:644-5
msgid "How do I save a document with another name?"
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.ol.li:646-7
msgid "Hover the mouse on the document name in the menu bar."
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.ol.li:647-7
msgid "Type the new file name in the text box and press <kbd>Enter</kbd>."
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.p:649-5
msgid "A copy of the document is saved with the new name in the same folder."
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.h3:652-5
msgid ""
"How can I quit <span class=\"productname\">{productname}</span> without "
"saving my edits?"
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.p:653-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"productname\">{productname}</span> saves the document in the "
"background regularly, you can't just close without saving it. To abandon "
"your changes, you must either undo them, or use the <span class=\"ui\""
">Revision History </span> in the <span class=\"ui\">File</span> menu."
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.h4:656-5
msgid ""
"Can <span class=\"productname\">{productname}</span> open a password-"
"protected document?"
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.p:657-5
msgid ""
"Yes. <span class=\"productname\">{productname}</span> opens password-"
"protected documents, but it is necessary to supply the password in the “"
"Enter password” prompt at load time."
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.h4:660-5
msgid "How can I check spelling in my language?"
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.p:661-5
msgid ""
"Choose menu <span class=\"ui\">Tools</span> → <span class=\"ui\">Languages</"
"span> and select the language for the whole document. Optionally you can set "
"languages for the selected text and for the current paragraph."
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.h4:664-5
msgid "How can I remove the red wavy lines in my document?"
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.p:665-5
msgid ""
"Choose menu <span class=\"ui\">Tools</span> and uncheck <span class=\"ui\""
">Automatic Spell Checking</span>."
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.h4:668-5
msgid "What is the blue wavy underline in some words in the text?"
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.p:669-5
msgid ""
"Grammar errors in the text are marked with the blue wavy underline. Click on "
"the underlined text with the right mouse button to open a menu with "
"suggestions to correct the grammar error and the offending grammar rules. "
"Select the right suggestion to change the text."
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.h4:672-5
msgid "Is there a thesaurus?"
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.p:673-5
msgid ""
"Yes. Click in the word you want and choose <span class=\"ui\">Tools</span> → "
"<span class=\"ui\">Thesaurus</span>. A dialog opens with many suggestions "
"for replacements."
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.img[alt]:674-29
msgid ""
"Thesaurus dialog for the word company, listing alternatives such as "
"institution, establishment, and troupe, with a Replace with field"
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.h4:677-5
msgid ""
"What are the blue <span class=\"blue\">¶</span> symbols and how can I remove "
"them from my text document?"
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.p:678-5
msgid ""
"The <span class=\"blue\">¶</span> symbol is a formatting mark. It is used to "
"help text alignment and editing and is not printed. To toggle it in the "
"document display, choose menu <span class=\"ui\">View</span> → <span class="
"\"ui\">Formatting mark</span>."
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.h4:685-5
msgid "How do I get a word count of my document?"
msgstr "Kaip sužinoti žodžių skaičių mano dokumente?"

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.p:686-5
msgid ""
"Word count is available in <span class=\"ui\">Tools</span> → <span class=\"ui"
"\">Word count</span>. A dialog shows word counts for selection and for the "
"whole document."
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.div.img[alt]:687-29
msgid ""
"Word Count dialog showing word and character counts for the current "
"selection and for the whole document"
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.p:688-5
msgid ""
"Word count is also displayed in the status bar. If no text is selected the "
"word count is for the whole document. Otherwise the word count is for the "
"selected text."
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.h4:691-5
msgid ""
"How can I insert a currency, copyright or trademark symbol in the document?"
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.p:692-5
msgid ""
"You can insert these special characters in the document using the <span "
"class=\"ui\">Special Character</span> dialog."
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.ol.li:694-7
msgid "Place the cursor in the position to insert the character."
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.ol.li:695-7
msgid ""
"Choose <span class=\"ui\">Insert</span> → <span class=\"ui\">Special "
"Characters </span> or click the corresponding icon in the toolbar. A dialog "
"opens."
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.ol.div.img[alt]:698-31
msgid ""
"Special Characters dialog with a character grid, search and font fields, "
"hexadecimal and decimal code inputs, and recent and favorite characters at "
"the bottom"
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.ol.li:699-7
msgid ""
"You can either browse the characters displayed with the drop lists or type a "
"search key in the <span class=\"ui\">Search</span> box. If you know the "
"Unicode numeric code of the special character, enter in the boxes on the "
"right."
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.ol.li:700-7
msgid ""
"Press <span class=\"ui\">Insert</span> button. To close the dialog, press "
"<span class=\"ui\">Cancel</span>."
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.h4:704-5
msgid "Why can't I delete text? It just gets a strike-through?"
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.p:705-5
msgid ""
"You have the Track Changes feature enabled for the document. Track Changes "
"records all changes in the text and shows the edits for later revision. "
"Useful for marking changes in text and spreadsheets. Track changes are "
"enabled choosing <span class=\"ui\">Edit</span> → <span class=\"ui\">Track "
"Changes </span> → <span class=\"ui\">Record</span>."
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.p:706-5
msgid ""
"With track changes enabled your document is shown in the following manner:"
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.ul.li:708-7
msgid "Deletions are marked with colored strike-through characters."
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.ul.li:709-7
msgid "Additions are marked with colored underlined characters."
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.ul.li:710-7
msgid "All changes are marked with a vertical bar in the right margin."
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.ul.li:711-7
msgid "Changes are displayed as comment in the right of the document area."
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.p:714-5
msgid ""
"The color assigned to the changes depends on the user that changes the "
"document."
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.p:715-5
msgid ""
"To display or hide track changes choose <span class=\"ui\">Edit</span> → "
"<span class=\"ui\">Track Changes </span> → <span class=\"ui\">Show</span>. "
"Beware that if track changes are enabled but hidden, you still record "
"changes and may inadvertently leave unwanted text available in the document."
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.p:716-5
msgid ""
"Changes can be accepted or rejected. To accept or reject changes, click on "
"the corresponding icons in the comment box on the right of the document. "
"Alternatively, choose <span class=\"ui\">Edit</span> → <span class=\"ui\""
">Track Changes </span> → <span class=\"ui\">Accept</span> or <span class=\"ui"
"\">Reject</span>. Furthermore, if you need to filter changes before "
"accepting or rejecting, choose <span class=\"ui\">Edit</span> → <span class="
"\"ui\">Track Changes </span> → <span class=\"ui\">Manage</span>. A dialog "
"shows a list of all tracked changes. Use the dialog buttons accordingly."
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.div.img[alt]:717-29
msgid ""
"Manage Changes dialog with a list of tracked changes showing action, author, "
"date, and comment columns, and Accept, Reject, Accept All, Reject All buttons"
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.h4:720-5
msgid "How do I set the margins of the document?"
msgstr "Kaip nustatyti dokumento paraštes?"

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.p:721-5
msgid ""
"Using the ruler drag the leftmost edge of the ruler to adjust the left "
"margin, or the rightmost for the right margin."
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.p:722-5
msgid "Using the page style"
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.ol.li:724-7
msgid ""
"Choose <span class=\"ui\">Format</span> → <span class=\"ui\">Page</span> and "
"select the <span class=\"ui\">Page</span> tab"
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.ol.li:725-7
msgid "Set the page margins in the dialog."
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.div.img[alt]:727-29
msgid ""
"Page Style dialog on the Organizer tab showing style name, next style, "
"inherit from, and category fields, with a summary of page properties"
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.h4:730-5
msgid "How do I change the page orientation to landscape inside my document?"
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.ol.li:732-7
msgid ""
"Place the cursor at the place where the page orientation is to change. Add "
"an empty paragraph."
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.ol.li:733-7
msgid ""
"Choose <span class=\"ui\">Format</span> → <span class=\"ui\">Paragraph</"
"span>, <span class=\"ui\">Text Flow </span> tab"
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.ol.li:734-7
msgid ""
"In the <span class=\"ui\">Breaks</span> area, mark Insert, Type: Page Break, "
"Position: Before."
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.ol.li:735-7
msgid "Select Landscape in “With Page Style”"
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.ol.li:736-7
msgid "Select if you want to change page numbering."
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.p:738-5
msgid ""
"To return to portrait orientation, repeat the procedure, choosing Portrait "
"in “With page style”."
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.h4:741-5
msgid "How can I make the new text look like other existing text?"
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.p:742-5
msgid "Directly:"
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.ol.li:744-7
msgid "Select the text with the existing format"
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.ol.li:745-7
#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.ol.li:787-7
msgid ""
"Click on the clone formatting icon <img alt=\"format paintbrush\" class"
"=\"icon-size\" src=\"images/lc_formatpaintbrush.svg\" />. The mouse pointer "
"turns to a paint bucket."
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.ol.li:746-7
msgid "Select the text you want to apply the new format."
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.p:750-5
msgid "Applying a paragraph style:"
msgstr "Pastraipos stiliaus taikymas:"

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.ol.li:752-7
msgid "Place the cursor at the paragraph to be formatted"
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.ol.li:753-7
msgid ""
"Select the style to apply in the style dropdown list. The paragraph displays "
"the styles attributes."
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.h4:757-5
msgid ""
"Why did the text I just typed change automatically? How can I revert it?"
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.p:758-5
msgid ""
"You have the AutoCorrection enabled. AutoCorrection compares the text just "
"typed to an internal table of text. In most cases, AutoCorrection corrects "
"typos while you type. If AutoCorrection is not necessary, disable it in "
"<span class=\"ui\">Tools</span> → <span class=\"ui\">AutoCorrection</span> → "
"<span class=\"ui\">While typing</span>."
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.h4:766-5
msgid "How can I select data to print?"
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.p:767-5
msgid ""
"Insert column and row breaks in the spreadsheet to narrow the print range "
"and print the document to download. On printing the PDF, select the pages of "
"interest."
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.h4:770-5
msgid "How can I import CSV data?"
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.ol.li:772-7
msgid ""
"Load your CSV data in some native tool to your platform, select and copy it "
"to the clipboard"
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.ol.li:773-7
msgid ""
"Activate the <span class=\"productname\">{productname}</span> spreadsheet "
"window."
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.ol.li:774-7
msgid ""
"Paste from the browser <span class=\"ui\">Edit</span> → <span class=\"ui\""
">Paste</span> or press <kbd>Ctrl</kbd><span class=\"kbd--plus\" aria-hidden="
"\"true\">+</span><kbd>V</kbd>. The <span class=\"ui\">Text Import</span> "
"dialog opens to let you describe the precise format of the CSV data."
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.ol.div.img[alt]:777-31
msgid ""
"Text Import dialog with character set, locale, separator options, and a "
"preview of the imported CSV data"
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.ol.li:778-7
msgid ""
"Select the character set, language and separator options for the CSV file."
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.p:780-5
msgid ""
"The CSV data is loaded into the selected cell where you pasted, according to "
"these settings."
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.h4:783-5
msgid "How can I copy the formatting of existing cells to new ones?"
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.p:784-5
msgid "This is easy to do using the Paintbrush tool in the toolbar."
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.ol.li:786-7
msgid "Format the source cell with the font, color background and more."
msgstr ""

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.div.ol.li:788-7
msgid "Select the cells you want to format. Release the mouse button."
